    <item>
      <title>AMD 称新款 AI 芯片即将问世，且表现有望超越 Nvidia</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/amd-says-new-ai-chips-will-be-out-soon-and-can-outperform-nvidia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国超微半导体公司 (Advanced Micro Devices Inc.) 希望在利润丰厚的人工智能处理器市场上赶超英伟达公司 (Nvidia Corp.)。该公司表示，其最新芯片正在向数据中心推出，并将在某些功能上超越其竞争对手。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/amd-says-new-ai-chips-will-be-out-soon-and-can-outperform-nvidia</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 16:45:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>传奇影业正在洽谈收购万达在《沙丘》工作室的股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/legendary-said-in-talks-to-buy-wanda-s-stake-in-dune-studio</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，传奇娱乐有限责任公司 (Legendary Entertainment LLC) 正就收购大连万达集团股份有限公司所持电影制片厂的股份进行深入谈判，这家中国企业集团正寻求撤销其最引人注目的海外收购之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/legendary-said-in-talks-to-buy-wanda-s-stake-in-dune-studio</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 16:32:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Altice 向债权人提供高达 15% 的股份作为减记回报</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/altice-offers-creditors-up-to-15-stake-in-return-for-haircut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[目前，陷入困境的电信巨头 Altice France 正试图削减其 244 亿欧元（267 亿美元）的债务，该公司正在提出一项提案，向有担保债权人提供公司股份，以使他们同意对其持股进行减记。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/altice-offers-creditors-up-to-15-stake-in-return-for-haircut</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 15:51:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马里解除对马斯克 SpaceX 的禁令，以控制 Starlink 的使用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/mali-lifts-ban-on-musk-s-spacex-in-bid-to-control-starlink-usage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马里军方领导层解除了对 SpaceX Starlink 卫星互联网套件销售和进口的禁令，该禁令是由于担心这些设备可能被伊斯兰激进分子和分离主义叛乱分子利用而实施的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/mali-lifts-ban-on-musk-s-spacex-in-bid-to-control-starlink-usage</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 15:42:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
